OL,3,CMan jailed for stabbing his own father
OL,4,Cin the chest
OL,6,FA 37-year-old man has been jailed for
OL,7,Fmore than five years after stabbing
OL,8,Fhis own father.
OL,10,FAndrew Roberts appeared at Liverpool
OL,11,FCrown Court on 19 June, after pleading
OL,12,Fguilty to Section 18 wounding with
OL,13,Fintent.
OL,15,FOfficers were called to an address on
OL,16,FBig Meadow Road in Woodchurch, on the
OL,17,FWirral, after reports that a 56-year-
OL,18,Fold man had suffered an injury to his
OL,19,Fchest.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
