OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,364,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1781892673
OL,3,CMan jailed for stabbing his own father
OL,4,Cin the chest
OL,6,FThe victim, who is Roberts' father,
OL,7,Fwas taken to hospital for treatment,
OL,8,Fwhich was not life-threatening.
OL,10,FRoberts, of Woodward Road in Rock
OL,11,FFerry, was found in the Rake Lane area
OL,12,Fand arrested following an
OL,13,Finvestigation.
OL,15,FHe was initially charged with
OL,16,Fattempted murder, but instead pleaded
OL,17,Fguilty to Section 18 assault.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
