OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,364,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1781892673
OL,3,CMan jailed for stabbing his own father
OL,4,Cin the chest
OL,6,FThe Crown Prosecution Service refused
OL,7,Fto accept his plea, and the case went
OL,8,Fto trial in May, resulting in a hung
OL,9,Fjury.
OL,11,FDetective Sergeant Ciara Cross said:
OL,12,F"This is an awful case where Roberts
OL,13,Fattacked his own father with a knife,
OL,14,Fwhich caused the victim to fear for
OL,15,Fhis life from his own son.
OL,17,F"The emotional impact this has had on
OL,18,Fthe victim has been extremely
OL,19,Fdistressing for him.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,364,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1781892673
OL,3,CMan jailed for stabbing his own father
OL,4,Cin the chest
OL,6,F"I hope Roberts uses the time behind
OL,7,Fbars to reflect on the severity of
OL,8,Fwhat he did, and the distress he has
OL,9,Fcaused to his father."
OL,11,FThe detective added: "The use of
OL,12,Fknives can have devastating
OL,13,Fconsequences, including domestic
OL,14,Fsettings such as this.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@VO]sD@VOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
