OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1781892673
OL,3,CMan jailed for stabbing his own father
OL,4,Cin the chest
OL,6,F"We are committed to removing anyone
OL,7,Fwho stores, carries and uses weapons,
OL,8,Fthrough proactive use of stop and
OL,9,Fsearch powers, open land searches,
OL,10,Fwarrants and education work alongside
OL,11,Fpartners. We continue to seek out
OL,12,Fthose involved in knife crime."
